item.title: Inbal Segev performs Bach's Cello Suite No. 1 in G major: Prelude
item.description:
Inbal Segev performs Bach's Cello Suite No. 1 in G major: Prelude

Cellist Inbal Segev performs the Prelude from Bach's Cello Suite No. 1 in G major on a Manhattan rooftop. Inbal Segev: Bach Cello Suites is available September 18 (US) and November 5 (worldwide) on Vox Classics.
